resources.string: Lolu hlelo lokusebenza luhunyushwe yi-Google Translate. IsiNgisi siwulimi lokuqala lwalolu hlelo lokusebenza. Sicela ukhumbule ukuthi kungase kube namaphutha ekuhumusheni.
